item.name: Dashboard

request.description: Get all sites with coordinates and pipe connections for map display. Returns sites array, pipes array (from site_relations), and legend for colors.

response.name: Get Map Locations

request.description: Get distribution data for donut/pie chart. Groups data by supplier or plant with percentage calculations.
Get distribution data grouped by pembangkit (power plant).
Get top 5 suppliers by Realisasi/TOP percentage. Returns ranked list with siteId, name, value (%), and percentage.
Get top 5 pembangkit (power plants) by MMBTU volume. Returns ranked list with siteId, name, value, and percentage.

query.description: Required. End date (same as start for hourly)

request.description: Get hourly flow chart data. Returns time series for each site, reference lines (JPH, TOP, Mean), summary stats, and period summaries.

query.description: Required. End date (same as start for hourly)

request.description: Get daily flow chart data grouped by supplier.
Get monthly flow chart data for yearly view.

query.description: Optional. Get specific contract by ID

request.description: Get contract information panel data. Returns contract details including jenis kontrak, nomor kontrak, jangka waktu, volume JPH/TOP, harga PJBG, and unit yang dipasok.

query.description: Optional. Get specific contract by ID

request.description: Get operational events / Catatan Kejadian timeline. Returns paginated list of events with site name, occurred time, title, description, and severity.
Get available filter options for dashboard dropdowns. Returns pemasok list, pembangkit list, transportir list, regions, and severities.
Get enhanced dashboard summary metrics. Returns period, total volume, contract counts, relation counts, and reconciliation stats.
[Legacy] Get daily volume data. Use /chart/flow with granularity=day instead.
[Legacy] Get hourly volume data. Use /chart/flow with granularity=hour instead.
